        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2012-04-13 21:59:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nThanks for updating the patch.  Sorry to not be clear in the precious inspection.\n\nThe configure check needs to be located in kernel version order in the lustre_core.m4 file, and have a comment that indicates what kernel version the API was added. This makes it easier to remove old checks and their compatibility code in the future when support for the old kernels is dropped.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
